{"tid":2346646,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"時代終結《東地》《新假期》《新Monday》停刊","createTime":"2020-12-30T11:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T16:18:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":38,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"37d3fd88088c23417478d275c1bfad17336eeb22","tid":2346646,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:41:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/MXVK5WQY4NG65OFRVNWVT5LGPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FMXVK5WQY4NG65OFRVNWVT5LGPY%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSLBzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=e2fe986c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FMXVK5WQY4NG65OFRVNWVT5LGPY%2F&h=948d5420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/MXVK5WQY4NG65OFRVNWVT5LGPY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n時代終結《東地》《新假期》《新Monday》停刊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/__ScWkjkqDEnWt4dTafdy1pv0SE=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BD3FFEVS6FEEDLVDMVEU2B6MBY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F__ScWkjkqDEnWt4dTafdy1pv0SE%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBD3FFEVS6FEEDLVDMVEU2B6MBY.jpg&h=2162c477&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■新傳媒旗下雜誌曾為全港閱讀人數最多的周刊。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】紙媒日漸萎縮，近30年歷史的娛樂雜誌《東方新地》連同新傳媒旗下的《新假期》和《新Monday》，將於2021年1月1日起停止印刷實體版。文字的溫度逐漸被數碼化的字體取代，有學者指出，手機化及無紙化為全球大趨勢，但相信報刊產業「如果跟住個Trend走，仍然係有得做」。<br />\n<br />\n新傳媒集團表示，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有《新假期》員工表示，公司未有公佈停刊原因，估計與廣告收益減少而須轉型有關，公司內部亦傳出實體書部門有數名同事因此需要離職。《東方新地》最後一期將會於明日出版，而《新假期》將由周刊轉為每季獨立出版，並與網上旅遊平台「GoTrip」合作，將於2021年3月推出春季號，售價為30元一本。新傳媒在1999年創辦《新假期》，其後兩年陸續收購雜誌，包括《新Monday》，以及向東方報業集團購入《東方新地》，三本刊物均由英皇旗下的新傳媒集團管理。內地企業恆大集團於2014年以9.5億元向英皇購入新傳媒七成半股份，成為該集團的主要股東。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呂秉權：跟Trend走仍有得做<br />\n<br />\n2016年，新傳媒將三本雜誌合併發行，其後集團裁員至少100人。三本刊物合而為一後，根據尼爾森媒介指標於2016年發佈的中期報告，它們一度成為全港閱讀人數最多的周刊，其中《新假期》出版的旅遊書籍全球銷量逾600萬本，亦曾引領社會發掘「隱世」美食的潮流。<br />\n<br />\n香港浸會大學新聞系高級講師呂秉權認為，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n全港報販大聯盟主席廖社青表示，《新假期》在同類型的刊物鶴立雞群，至合併後銷量仍長佔第一。對於停刊消息，他認為須認清事實，未來只會有更多實體刊物停刊，報販收入將進一步受打擊，「少咗產品賣就少咗錢收」，未來應轉型如配合旅遊業發展尋找出路。"},{"pid":"5968a0b82a9105a10c93372641c60877cc2744f5","tid":2346646,"uid":211466,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:42:40.000Z","msg":"我屌鳩你新假期"},{"pid":"cb179ce89b7e3bc7b46e816de2b6a1e364726a09","tid":2346646,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5968a0b82a9105a10c93372641c60877cc2744f5","tid":2346646,"uid":211466,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:42:40.000Z","msg":"我屌鳩你新假期"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:43:29.000Z","msg":"生態災難<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e6da914ff53341fdc831034b34a4390deca866","tid":2346646,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:43:40.000Z","msg":"係唔係白粉報㗎？"},{"pid":"8b15090c12aeec5248aefb55aff0976105b5c59e","tid":2346646,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:43:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c66bd5a4d64c266e6abdbee50bca0f6d3a7db71e","tid":2346646,"uid":321345,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b15090c12aeec5248aefb55aff0976105b5c59e","tid":2346646,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:43:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:44:30.000Z","msg":"白粉"},{"pid":"e969bb53813bd36468122a50d675d5d253a36ca5","tid":2346646,"uid":20867,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:45:05.000Z","msg":"終於頂唔住<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">香港中古廣告: 東方新地 頂唔住(周星馳)1991<br />\n206,434 views</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=camdVPz9atE\" da